                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "column": 1,
                        "order": 2,
                        "content": "**Edit menu:**\n1. Click on 'Navigation Edit'\n2. Choose menu type (Mega Menu or Dropdown)\n3. Add items with 'Add Item'\n4. Drag items to reorder\n5. Click 'Save'\n\n**Sub-items:** Create nested menus for complex structures."
